commit.title: Add a script for pinning third-party developments
commit.message:
Add a script for pinning third-party developments

The “pin-plugins.ml” program, to be called in its own directory, can be used at
release time to fix the references to third-party developments to their current
version; these developments are used in CI and in the Windows installer.
